WEBVTT

00:00:19.162 --> 00:00:24.349
♪The whole world is lit up♪

00:00:24.350 --> 00:00:25.661
♪Because you exist♪

00:00:25.662 --> 00:00:27.741
♪You're always♪

00:00:27.742 --> 00:00:32.391
♪Somewhere close, flying with me♪

00:00:32.392 --> 00:00:35.124
♪Go to where the wind blows♪

00:00:35.125 --> 00:00:36.691
♪Hold tight♪

00:00:36.692 --> 00:00:42.481
♪To the ray of light that belongs to us♪

00:00:42.482 --> 00:00:47.932
=Wild & Fiery=
=Episode 11=

00:00:47.979 --> 00:00:49.698
Staying at home for a long period

00:00:49.699 --> 00:00:50.860
would actually be good for him.

00:00:51.140 --> 00:00:51.899
Well.

00:00:51.979 --> 00:00:52.698
Come with me.

00:00:52.699 --> 00:00:54.378
Let's settle the discharge fee.

00:00:54.379 --> 00:00:55.939
I don't think he should be discharged.

00:01:00.900 --> 00:01:01.699
Doctor,

00:01:02.259 --> 00:01:04.338
I'm Mu Chen Zhou's wife

00:01:04.339 --> 00:01:05.618
and also his guardian.

00:01:05.619 --> 00:01:07.459
As his guardian, I'm telling you

00:01:07.859 --> 00:01:09.539
that I do not allow him
to be discharged.

00:01:10.979 --> 00:01:12.400
Besides, he's still unconscious.

00:01:12.400 --> 00:01:14.000
If anything happens
after he leaves the hospital,

00:01:14.000 --> 00:01:15.299
can you take responsibility?

00:01:16.159 --> 00:01:17.939
Can your family discuss it
among yourselves first

00:01:17.940 --> 00:01:18.980
before making a decision?

00:01:20.540 --> 00:01:22.539
You're acting like
you own this hospital.

00:01:24.339 --> 00:01:25.459
Stepmom,

00:01:25.820 --> 00:01:27.099
you kept saying

00:01:27.100 --> 00:01:28.459
my dad was doing well before.

00:01:28.660 --> 00:01:30.299
Is this what you call doing well?

00:01:33.219 --> 00:01:35.459
His condition did improve
a little before,

00:01:35.699 --> 00:01:37.099
but for some reason,

00:01:37.300 --> 00:01:39.099
he suddenly fell unconscious recently.

00:01:39.300 --> 00:01:41.739
I had no choice but to transfer him
to this hospital.

00:01:42.979 --> 00:01:44.058
Besides,

00:01:44.059 --> 00:01:46.379
I didn't tell you because
I didn't want you to worry.

00:01:46.380 --> 00:01:47.340
Fine.

00:01:48.540 --> 00:01:51.340
You've worked hard
taking care of my dad all this time.

00:01:51.499 --> 00:01:53.019
Now that I'm back,

00:01:53.259 --> 00:01:55.420
I should fulfill my duty
as his daughter.

00:01:55.499 --> 00:01:57.539
I'm touched.

00:01:57.900 --> 00:01:59.418
If your dad knew

00:01:59.419 --> 00:02:01.099
you were always by his side,

00:02:02.540 --> 00:02:04.099
he would be comforted.

00:02:10.460 --> 00:02:11.939
(Xu Mingzhu, just you wait.)

00:02:12.059 --> 00:02:13.539
(I won't let you get away with this.)

00:02:20.900 --> 00:02:21.859
Who would've thought

00:02:21.860 --> 00:02:22.459
Mu Zhiyu

00:02:22.460 --> 00:02:24.180
would find this place so quickly?

00:02:27.180 --> 00:02:29.020
Something's wrong here.

00:02:29.260 --> 00:02:30.419
The most urgent thing now

00:02:31.539 --> 00:02:33.740
is making sure that the old man
never wakes up.

00:02:34.420 --> 00:02:35.819
If he wakes up,

00:02:35.860 --> 00:02:37.580
everything we've done will be exposed.

00:02:42.260 --> 00:02:44.539
Aren't you afraid your husband
might catch us at your house?

00:02:44.939 --> 00:02:46.019
Relax.

00:02:46.020 --> 00:02:47.340
He's in the office.

00:02:51.619 --> 00:02:52.300
You two!

00:02:52.779 --> 00:02:53.778
What are you doing?

00:02:53.779 --> 00:02:54.740
Dear!

00:02:55.219 --> 00:02:56.539
Why are you back?

00:02:57.020 --> 00:02:58.180
Mr. Mu...

00:02:58.580 --> 00:02:59.979
This is all a misunderstanding.

00:03:00.260 --> 00:03:02.060
You shameless pair!

00:03:02.099 --> 00:03:02.979
You've disgraced

00:03:02.980 --> 00:03:04.699
the Mu family.

00:03:11.099 --> 00:03:12.460
Mr. Mu...

00:03:17.860 --> 00:03:19.979
Do whatever you have to do.

00:03:20.180 --> 00:03:21.979
Make sure he can't say a thing

00:03:22.020 --> 00:03:23.539
like before.

00:03:25.260 --> 00:03:26.539
I'll figure something out.

00:03:36.420 --> 00:03:38.019
You haven't rested properly lately.

00:03:38.020 --> 00:03:39.379
Get some sleep.

00:03:39.420 --> 00:03:40.659
I'll watch over things here.

00:03:42.700 --> 00:03:43.780
It's fine.

00:03:44.260 --> 00:03:45.220
I'm not tired.

00:03:48.860 --> 00:03:51.060
It's been a long time

00:03:51.300 --> 00:03:53.900
since I've quietly shared the same space
with my dad like this.

00:03:58.420 --> 00:03:59.340
Back then,

00:03:59.659 --> 00:04:01.139
when I insisted on going abroad,

00:04:02.339 --> 00:04:03.939
he silently supported me

00:04:04.580 --> 00:04:05.500
and encouraged me.

00:04:08.499 --> 00:04:09.740
Unfortunately,

00:04:10.939 --> 00:04:12.659
I was too proud to lose.

00:04:13.180 --> 00:04:15.819
I never showed him any care.

00:04:30.659 --> 00:04:32.179
What's past is past.

00:04:33.020 --> 00:04:34.460
At least now

00:04:34.659 --> 00:04:36.220
you can still stay by his side.

00:04:43.620 --> 00:04:45.658
(This old geezer is pretty tough.)

00:04:45.659 --> 00:04:48.259
(Tonight, I'll give you the rest
of the sedative)

00:04:48.260 --> 00:04:50.419
(and shut you up for good.)

00:04:50.659 --> 00:04:53.099
(No chance of you waking up
and ruining our plans.)

00:04:57.659 --> 00:04:58.859
Did you receive everything?

00:05:00.060 --> 00:05:01.059
Take it

00:05:01.380 --> 00:05:03.179
and run a DNA test for me.

00:05:03.580 --> 00:05:04.338
Boss,

00:05:04.339 --> 00:05:05.780
who are you testing against?

00:05:05.859 --> 00:05:08.140
Everything's been so mysterious
since you came back.

00:05:08.140 --> 00:05:10.000
Don't ask about things
that aren't your business.

00:05:10.000 --> 00:05:11.859
Yes, Boss. I'll take care of it right away.

00:05:26.060 --> 00:05:28.499
Weren't you staying at the hospital
taking care of the chairman?

00:05:28.850 --> 00:05:30.800
How do you suddenly have time
to come to the office?

00:05:31.339 --> 00:05:32.340
I came here

00:05:32.380 --> 00:05:34.979
to explain the situation to the board.

00:05:36.260 --> 00:05:37.099
Ms. Xu,

00:05:37.380 --> 00:05:38.979
you hid my dad.

00:05:39.925 --> 00:05:41.326
What exactly are you planning?

00:05:43.380 --> 00:05:45.260
You must be joking.

00:05:46.140 --> 00:05:48.179
Then who's the person in the hospital?

00:05:49.659 --> 00:05:51.699
I went through so much to find him

00:05:51.700 --> 00:05:53.900
only to discover he's been unconscious
the whole time.

00:05:54.539 --> 00:05:55.859
Strange enough,

00:05:56.380 --> 00:05:57.379
in the video

00:05:57.380 --> 00:05:59.979
you released a few days ago,
he looked perfectly conscious.

00:06:02.580 --> 00:06:05.179
But the moment I found him,
he became like this.

00:06:06.940 --> 00:06:07.900
Ms. Xu,

00:06:09.099 --> 00:06:11.059
did you fail to take good care of him,

00:06:11.900 --> 00:06:13.940
or was that video fake to begin with?

00:06:25.900 --> 00:06:26.859
Ms. Xu,

00:06:27.179 --> 00:06:28.699
according to Zhiyu's claim,

00:06:28.700 --> 00:06:31.059
were you really conveying
Chairman Mu's instructions,

00:06:31.060 --> 00:06:32.940
or just acting on your personal motives?

00:06:36.779 --> 00:06:39.059
I admit the video was fake.

00:06:39.140 --> 00:06:41.178
But I did it for the company.

00:06:41.179 --> 00:06:43.379
The chairman's condition
has always been unstable.

00:06:43.380 --> 00:06:45.059
He was doing fine earlier,

00:06:45.060 --> 00:06:47.499
but suddenly fell unconscious.

00:06:47.779 --> 00:06:48.899
Besides,

00:06:48.900 --> 00:06:51.099
the company's stock price
has been dropping.

00:06:51.500 --> 00:06:52.778
If the public

00:06:52.779 --> 00:06:54.460
found out the truth,

00:06:55.237 --> 00:06:57.596
aren't you afraid the company
would collapse?

00:06:59.700 --> 00:07:01.379
I'm truly moved

00:07:01.380 --> 00:07:03.140
by what you said.

00:07:06.700 --> 00:07:08.020
If the public found out,

00:07:08.219 --> 00:07:09.419
it would cause trouble.

00:07:10.380 --> 00:07:14.511
But the report shows my dad fell unconscious
because he was injected with unknown drugs

00:07:14.512 --> 00:07:15.832
over a long period of time.

00:07:16.020 --> 00:07:17.419
What, Ms. Xu?

00:07:18.739 --> 00:07:20.499
Was that also
for the sake of the company?

00:07:23.820 --> 00:07:25.900
What does that have to do with me?

00:07:25.940 --> 00:07:26.978
How could I possibly

00:07:26.979 --> 00:07:28.900
(Suddenly went into a coma)
keep Chenzhou from waking up?

00:07:29.380 --> 00:07:30.460
Ms. Xu,

00:07:30.900 --> 00:07:32.900
how do you explain this?

00:07:37.820 --> 00:07:39.220
Once my dad wakes up,

00:07:39.900 --> 00:07:41.499
everything will become clear.

00:07:42.179 --> 00:07:43.739
I don't mind waiting a few more days.

00:07:45.900 --> 00:07:48.299
Mu Zhiyu really doesn't know her place.

00:07:48.580 --> 00:07:51.220
Just because she found Mu Chenzhou,
she thinks she can boss me around?

00:07:51.299 --> 00:07:53.139
Ms. Xu, Mu Chenzhou hasn't woken up yet.

00:07:53.140 --> 00:07:54.260
We still have a chance.

00:07:55.260 --> 00:07:56.379
Once he wakes up,

00:07:56.380 --> 00:07:57.700
we're finished.

00:08:07.580 --> 00:08:09.020
At this point,

00:08:09.859 --> 00:08:12.539
the only option is to make sure
he stays silent forever.

00:08:12.900 --> 00:08:15.820
(Silence him for good.)

00:08:25.659 --> 00:08:27.299
You should smile more often.

00:08:31.020 --> 00:08:33.180
I'll take that as a compliment.

00:08:33.539 --> 00:08:35.180
Looks like you're in a good mood today.

00:08:37.419 --> 00:08:39.460
I shut my stepmom down

00:08:39.539 --> 00:08:41.180
and found my dad.

00:08:41.340 --> 00:08:42.739
Of course I'm happy.

00:09:05.380 --> 00:09:07.899
Now we just have to wait
for your dad to wake up,

00:09:07.900 --> 00:09:09.139
and everything will be clear.

00:09:11.620 --> 00:09:14.820
There are many documents here.
Let's pack them up and take them back.

00:09:26.260 --> 00:09:27.180
What?

00:09:27.939 --> 00:09:29.180
Something happened to my dad?

00:09:40.575 --> 00:09:44.805
♪Light comes beaming in♪

00:09:44.945 --> 00:09:49.314
♪Landing on my skin♪

00:09:49.315 --> 00:09:53.805
♪Warms the space you left behind♪

00:09:58.025 --> 00:10:01.964
♪Shadows move around♪

00:10:01.965 --> 00:10:06.574
♪Awake, racing thoughts♪

00:10:06.575 --> 00:10:11.105
♪Try to keep the memories safe♪

00:10:14.705 --> 00:10:20.495
♪Don't slip away♪

00:10:22.945 --> 00:10:27.514
♪I'm all yours, all yours♪

00:10:27.515 --> 00:10:31.914
♪I'm all yours, all yours♪

00:10:31.915 --> 00:10:36.235
♪I'm all yours, all yours♪

00:10:36.255 --> 00:10:40.235
♪I'm all yours, all yours♪

00:10:40.705 --> 00:10:45.014
♪I'm all yours, all yours♪

00:10:45.015 --> 00:10:49.344
♪I'm all yours, all yours♪

00:10:49.345 --> 00:10:53.654
♪I'm all yours, all yours♪

00:10:53.655 --> 00:10:59.805
♪I'm all yours, all yours♪